<p class=3D"mw-empty-elt">

</p><p>In <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linear_algebra" title=3D=
"Linear algebra">linear algebra</a>, an <b>eigenvector</b> (<span class=3D"=
rt-commentedText nowrap"><span class=3D"IPA nopopups noexcerpt" lang=3D"en-=
fonipa"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA/English" title=3D=
