</span> matrix <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">A<=
/span>, then the eigenvalue equation for a linear transformation above can =
be rewritten as the matrix multiplication
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
