 so <span class=3D"texhtml"><b>x</b></span> is an eigenvector of <span clas=
s=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">A</span>.</figcaption></fig=
ure>
<p>Consider <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">n</sp=
