>determinant</a> of the matrix <span class=3D"texhtml">(<i>A</i> =E2=88=92 =
<i>=CE=BBI</i>)</span> is zero. Therefore, the eigenvalues of <span class=
=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">A</span> are values of <span=
 class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">=CE=BB</span> that sat=
isfy the equation
</p>
