</p><p>Setting the characteristic polynomial equal to zero, it has roots at=
 <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>=CE=BB</i> =3D 1</span> and <span class=3D"texh=
tml"><i>=CE=BB</i> =3D 3</span>, which are the two eigenvalues of <span cla=
