{\lambda =3D1}=3D{\begin{bmatrix}1\\-1\end{bmatrix}},\quad \mathbf {v} _{\l=
ambda =3D3}=3D{\begin{bmatrix}1\\1\end{bmatrix}}.}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
