<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Left_and_right_eigenvectors=
">Left and right eigenvectors</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span clas=
s=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/=
index.php?title=3DEigenvalues_and_eigenvectors&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;sectio=
