</p><p>For <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>=CE=BB</i> =3D 1</span>, equation (<b=
><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eigenvalues_and_eigenvectors#math=
_2">2</a></b>) becomes,
