s=3D"texhtml">[0 0 0 1]<sup>T</sup></span>. The total geometric multiplicit=
y <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>=CE=B3</i><sub><i>A</i></sub></span> is 2, whi=
ch is the smallest it could be for a matrix with two distinct eigenvalues. =
Geometric multiplicities are defined in a later section.
</p>
