ix}}=3D6\cdot {\begin{bmatrix}x\\y\end{bmatrix}}}"></span>
</p><p>This matrix equation is equivalent to two <a href=3D"https://en.wiki=
pedia.org/wiki/Linear_equation" title=3D"Linear equation">linear equations<=
/a>
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
